Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette occur in an adjoining classroom, where career counselors advise students, including international attendees, on maintaining eye contact and visa sponsorship requirements. As recruiters assess enthusiasm among attendees and fill interview sign-up sheets, volunteers begin stacking collapsed booths and gathering leftover brochures. The aroma of coffee and catered snacks wafts from the lounge, and a post-event survey link flashes on monitors near the exit.

Inside, colorful booths feature consulting firms with glossy case study booklets, tech companies showcasing live demos, and a cybersecurity firm running a password cracking challenge on a laptop. Healthcare providers share community outreach initiatives, while participants utilize tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes from branded folders. Many attendees exit clutching tote bags filled with notebooks, pens, and business cards from enthusiastic recruiters. Workshops on networking etiquette occur in an adjoining classroom, where international students seek advice on visa sponsorship. Volunteers stack collapsed booths, and camera crews capture interviews as career center staff log attendance on laptops. A post-event survey link is displayed on monitors near the exit.

summaries.108: As the day winds down at the university career fair in the gym, a busy atmosphere prevails, enhanced by the aroma of coffee and catered snacks from the lounge.
